---
---

<section class="relative pt-28 pb-16 lg:pt-36 lg:pb-24 min-h-screen flex items-center overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute -top-40 -left-40 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-brand-primary/5 blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-0 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-brand-accent/5 blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 w-full">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-8 items-center">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 text-center lg:text-left space-y-6">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 bg-brand-primary/10 text-brand-primary px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">
          <span>⚡ Energía Ancestral de Origen Peruano</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-brand-primary leading-none">
          Para ser el mejor, elige <span class="text-brand-accent">Puka Power</span>.
        </h1>

        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-brand-dark/80 font-normal leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0">
          El poder del rayo, ahora natural. Energía sostenida a base de <span class="font-bold text-brand-primary">cáscara de café, camu camu y maca andina</span>. Sin químicos, sin bajones.
        </p>

        <div class="pt-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4">
          <a href="/tienda" class="animate-pulse-btn w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-brand-accent text-brand-light font-extrabold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full hover:bg-brand-accentGold transition-all duration-300 text-center shadow-2xl shadow-brand-accent/40">
            Acepta el Reto de 3 Días
          </a>
          <a href="/#beneficios" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-transparent border-2 border-brand-primary/20 text-brand-primary font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full hover:bg-brand-primary hover:text-brand-light hover:border-brand-primary transition-all duration-300 text-center">
            Saber Más
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-8 border-t border-brand-primary/10 grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center lg:text-left">
          <div>
            <p class="font-serif text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-primary">100%</p>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-brand-dark/60 uppercase">Ingredientes Reales</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-serif text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-primary">0%</p>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-brand-dark/60 uppercase">Azúcar Añadida</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-serif text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-primary">24h</p>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-brand-dark/60 uppercase">Foco y Claridad</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex justify-center relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-brand-accent/20 to-brand-accentGold/20 rounded-full blur-3xl transform scale-75 -z-10 animate-pulse"></div>

        <div class="relative w-full max-w-[340px] sm:max-w-[400px]">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 bg-brand-accent text-brand-light font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg shadow-xl z-20 transform rotate-12">
            Envío Gratis hoy 🇵🇪
          </div>

          <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-primary/10 to-brand-primary/25 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-brand-light/30 backdrop-blur-sm overflow-hidden flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-48 h-80 relative flex items-center justify-center transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500 cursor-pointer">
              <img
                src="/sprites/Puka-Power.webp"
                alt="Lata de energía Puka Power - Hecha en Perú con cáscara de café, camu camu y maca andina"
                class="w-full h-full object-contain drop-shadow-[0_8px_24px_rgba(123,17,19,0.4)]"
                width="192"
                height="320"
                decoding="async"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="w-40 h-5 bg-black/30 rounded-full blur-md mt-6"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-brand-light p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-xl flex items-center space-x-3 border border-brand-primary/10">
            <span class="flex h-3 w-3 relative">
              <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-green-400 opacity-75"></span>
              <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-3 w-3 bg-green-500"></span>
            </span>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-dark">982 personas lo han probado hoy</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

